stanford.androidlib.graphics

Class GRect

  • java.lang.Object
    • stanford.androidlib.graphics.GObject
      • stanford.androidlib.graphics.GRect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GFillable, GResizable, GScalable

    public class GRect
extends GObject
implements GFillable, GResizable, GScalable
    The GRect class is a graphical object whose appearance consists of a rectangular box.
